# Technical Report

## Introduction
This project analyzes customer churn and sales data.

## Data Cleaning
- Removed duplicates
- Handled missing values
- Standardized dataset

## Exploratory Data Analysis
- Churn distribution analyzed
- Sales trends visualized
- Correlation heatmap created

## Statistical Analysis
Hypothesis testing performed using T-test.

## Machine Learning
Random Forest Classifier used for churn prediction.

## Results
Model achieved good prediction accuracy.

## Recommendations
- Retention strategies
- Marketing optimization
- Customer segmentation targeting

## Conclusion
Data-driven decisions can significantly improve business performance.